tanone, as well as pharma grade castor oil. The company also provides Jagrocos, Jagromul, Dermcare, Jagroil COCG series, Jagrolatum, Jagrowax CHS, Jagrosorb, and Jagrocid products. In addition, it engages in the power generation business. The company serves agriculture, cosmetics, electronics, lubricants, paints, perfumeries, pharmaceuticals, polymers and plastics, textiles, and rubber and construction industries. The company was incorporated in 1992 and is based in Mumbai, India. Jayant Agro-Organics Limited is a subsidiary of Jayant Finvest Limited."}}